BT /F2 18 Tf 54 730.00 Td (AQI Monitor Firmware Source Code Report) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 696.00 Td (This report explains the code in `src/`, `include/`, and `platformio.ini`.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 683.00 Td (It assumes you know web development and some Python, but are new to C, C++,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.00 Td (Arduino firmware, and header files.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 643.00 Td (1. Big Picture) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.00 Td (This project is firmware for an ESP8266 D1 Mini air quality monitor. Firmware is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 603.00 Td (software that runs directly on a microcontroller instead of inside a browser,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.00 Td (Node.js, or a desktop operating system.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 571.00 Td (The hardware pieces are:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.00 Td (- ESP8266 D1 Mini: the small Wi-Fi microcontroller board that runs the code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 539.00 Td (- PMS5003: a particulate matter sensor. It reports PM1.0, PM2.5, PM10, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.00 Td (  particle counts.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 513.00 Td (- MH-Z19E: a CO2 sensor. It reports carbon dioxide in ppm and a rough internal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.00 Td (  temperature.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 487.00 Td (- 2.4 inch SPI TFT display: the screen.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 474.00 Td (- Push button on D0: switches between display screens.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 455.00 Td (The firmware does four major jobs:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 436.00 Td (1. Read the PMS5003 particle sensor over serial.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 423.00 Td (2. Read the MH-Z19E CO2 sensor over serial.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.00 Td (3. Convert particle readings into US EPA AQI numbers and categories.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 397.00 Td (4. Draw a dashboard/details UI on the TFT screen.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 378.00 Td (The project is organized like this:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 355.00 Td (platformio.ini       Build configuration for PlatformIO.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 344.00 Td (include/config.h     Shared pin numbers, baud rates, timings, and options.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 333.00 Td (src/main.cpp         Main Arduino setup/loop and sensor scheduling.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 322.00 Td (src/pms5003.h/.cpp   Driver for the PMS5003 particle sensor.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 311.00 Td (src/mhz19.h/.cpp     Driver for the MH-Z19E CO2 sensor.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 300.00 Td (src/aqi.h/.cpp       AQI math and color/category helpers.) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 289.00 Td (src/ui.h/.cpp        Display data model and TFT drawing code.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 260.00 Td (2. Arduino and C++ Basics) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 227.00 Td (`.cpp` files) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 204.00 Td (`.cpp` files contain C++ implementation code. In web terms, think of them like) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 191.00 Td (JavaScript or TypeScript modules that contain the actual function bodies.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 172.00 Td (Example:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 149.00 Td (int aqiFromPm25\(float ugm3\) { return interpolate\(PM25_BP, 6, ugm3\); }) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 128.00 Td (This defines a function named `aqiFromPm25`.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 103.00 Td (`.h` files) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 80.00 Td (`.h` files are header files. They usually declare the public shape of code:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 67.00 Td (functions, classes, structs, constants, and types that other files are allowed) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
