BT /F1 10 Tf 54 133.00 Td (- `uint16_t`: unsigned 16-bit integer, 0 to 65535. Two bytes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 120.00 Td (- `uint32_t`: unsigned 32-bit integer, 0 to about 4.29 billion. Four bytes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 101.00 Td (The `u` means unsigned, so negative values are not allowed.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 76.00 Td (`constexpr`) Tj ET
