BT /F2 14 Tf 54 217.00 Td (14. Runtime Data Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 190.00 Td (The full runtime flow is:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 171.00 Td (1. `setup\(\)` starts serial logging, disables Wi-Fi, configures pins, starts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 158.00 Td (   SoftwareSerial ports, initializes the UI, configures CO2 ABC, and starts the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 145.00 Td (   first sensor cycle.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 132.00 Td (2. `loop\(\)` enters `PMS_LISTEN`.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 119.00 Td (3. `Pms5003::poll\(\)` reads PMS bytes until it finds a valid 32-byte frame.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 106.00 Td (4. `main.cpp` saves `PmsData` and switches to CO2.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 93.00 Td (5. `Mhz19::requestReading\(\)` sends a 9-byte command.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 80.00 Td (6. `Mhz19::poll\(\)` waits for a valid 9-byte response.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 67.00 Td (7. `publishReadings\(\)` builds a `UiModel`.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
