BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 133.00 Td (ui.cpp         = canvas-style UI renderer) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 122.00 Td (main.cpp       = app controller/event loop) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 54 111.00 Td (platformio.ini = package/build/deployment config) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 90.00 Td (Instead of HTTP requests, the "APIs" are UART byte streams.) Tj ET
